<item>
            <title>[TIKA-215] Use a thread pool in ParsingReader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-215</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently a new thread is created for each new ParsingReader instance. For better performance and manageability it would be good if the thread was allocated from a configurable thread pool.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
